title: Striking - Themeforest MultiFlex & Ecommerce Responsive - Wo
description:
Striking MulitFlex is an extremely powerful and flexible wordpress theme featuring a heavy duty framework that can scale for large sites and web requirements. It features true WP Multisite capability, is a WPML approved theme, and features customization for Woo Commerce plugin integration. 17,000+ Themeforest purchasers tell us it is the most feature laden and customizable theme they have ever used.

To install:
1. Upload the folder to the /wp-content/themes/ directory
2. Activate the theme through the 'Themes' menu in WordPress
